      <paragraph eId="para_1" class="MercuryDocument">
        <content eId="para_1__content">
          <p xml:space="preserve"> At its 49th plenary meeting, on 19 December 2023, the General Assembly, on the recommendation of the Second Committee,<authorialNote marker="1" placement="bottom" eId="authorialNote_1"><p xml:space="preserve"> <a href="https://undocs.org/en/A/78/468">A/78/468</a>, para. 7.</p></authorialNote> recalling its resolution <a href="https://undocs.org/en/A/RES/77/335">77/335</a> of 1 September 2023, in particular the provisions relating to working methods, as well as its decisions 74/537 B of 11 August 2020, 75/548 B of 29 July 2021 and 77/538 B of 24 July 2023, requested the Bureau of the Second Committee to convene up to two informal dialogues of the Committee in the first months of 2024 to discuss the working methods of the Committee and to update the conference room paper on the working methods of the Second Committee following those discussions. </p>
